        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "captain placed before my eyes a working drawing that gave the ground plan, cross section, and side view of the Nautilus.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Then he began his description as follows:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Here, Professor Aronnax, are the different dimensions of this boat now transporting you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "So it isn't quite built on the ten to one ratio of your high-speed steamers; but its lines are sufficiently long, and their tapering gradual enough, so that the displaced water easily slips past and poses no obstacle to the ship's movements.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"These two dimensions allow you to obtain, via a simple calculation, the surface area and volume of the Nautilus.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "So I was obliged not to exceed this weight while building it to the aforesaid dimensions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"The Nautilus is made up of two hulls, one inside the other; between them, joining them together, are iron T bars that give this ship the utmost rigidity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "In fact, thanks to this cellular arrangement, it has the resistance of a stone block, as if it were completely solid. Its plating can't give way; it's self adhering and not dependent on the tightness of its rivets; and due to the perfect union of its materials, the solidarity of its construction allows it to defy the most violent seas.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Clear?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Clear,\" I replied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "These ballast tanks exist within easy access in the lower reaches of the Nautilus.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Fine, captain, but now we come to a genuine difficulty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "You're able to lie flush with the surface of the ocean, that I understand. But lower down, while diving beneath that surface, isn't your submersible going to encounter a pressure, and consequently undergo an upward thrust, that must be assessed at one atmosphere per every thirty feet of water, hence at about one kilogram per each square centimeter?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Precisely, sir.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Then unless you fill up the whole Nautilus, I don't see how you can force it down into the heart of these liquid masses.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"I'm all ears, captain.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"That's obvious,\" I replied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Now then, if water isn't absolutely incompressible, at least it compresses very little.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "In fact, according to the most recent calculations, this reduction is only point zero zero zero zero four three six per atmosphere, or per every thirty feet of depth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Consequently, I'd have to increase my weight from one thousand five hundred seven point two metric tons to one thousand five hundred thirteen point seven seven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "So the added weight would only be six point five seven metric tons.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"That's all?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"I accept your calculations, captain,\" I replied, \"and I'd be ill mannered to dispute them, since your daily experience bears them out. But at this juncture, I have a hunch that we're still left with one real difficulty.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_36627_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/36627/5784_36627_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"What's that, sir?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"Let us consider the matter,\" I said to myself; \"we are going to ascend the Sneffels mountain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Well and good.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "We are about to pay a visit to the very bottom of the crater.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Good, still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Others have done it and did not perish from that course.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"That, however, is not the whole matter to be considered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Now, we have no evidence to prove that Sneffels is really extinct.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "What proof have we that an eruption is not shortly about to take place?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "Because the monster has slept soundly since twelve nineteen, does it follow that he is never to wake?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "\"If he does wake what is to become of us?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "These were questions worth thinking about, and upon them I reflected long and deeply.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "I could not lie down in search of sleep without dreaming of eruptions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5784_61948_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5784/61948/5784_61948_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5784",
        "content": "I sought him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
